User Management
Overview: Comprehensive user management with activity tracking and subscription assignment.
Features:
â€¢	User CRUD operations
â€¢	Advanced search and filters
â€¢	Bulk actions support
â€¢	Subscription assignment
â€¢	Activity monitoring
â€¢	Click tracking (username/password views)
Click Tracking Details:
â€¢	Tracks every click on "Show Password" button
â€¢	Tracks username copy actions
â€¢	Stores daily counts in user_activity_logs
â€¢	Resets daily at midnight
Key Functions:
â€¢	createUser() - Add new user with validation
â€¢	assignSubscription() - Assign user to subscription slot
â€¢	trackUserClick() - Record password/username views
â€¢	getUserActivityReport() - Generate activity reports
________________________________________
Subscription Management
Overview: Manage shared service accounts with flexible 11-column configuration system.
11-Column System:
1.	Service Name (Required)
2.	Icon (Required)
3.	Title (Required)
4.	Price (Required)
5.	Description (Optional - hidden if empty)
6.	Features (Optional)
7.	Validity (Optional)
8.	Support Info (Optional)
9.	Extra Info 1 (Optional)
10.	Extra Info 2 (Optional)
11.	Notes (Optional)
Connection Status:
â€¢	ğŸŸ¢ Green = Connected
â€¢	ğŸ”´ Red = Disconnected
â€¢	Auto-detection every 5 minutes
â€¢	One-click reconnection via "Get OTP"
OTP Pattern Support:
$patterns = [
    'numeric_6' => '/\b\d{6}\b/',              // 123456
    'alphanumeric' => '/\b[A-Z0-9]{6}\b/',     // ABC123
    'dash_format' => '/\d{4}-\d{4}/',          // 1234-5678
    'service_prefix' => '/NETFLIX-(\w+)/',     // NETFLIX-ABC123
];
